										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Impulse Gamer Interviews Katrina Garsten About Pillars II!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">March 15, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Producer, Katrina Garsten, <a href="http://www.impulsegamer.com/katrina-garsten-interview-pillars-eternity-ii-deadfire/" target="_blank">recently sat</a> with Impulse Gamer to discuss the game and what it has been like working on the project.</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Update 45 Is Now Live!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">February 23, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	We are happy to announce that Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Backer Update 45 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oj4DNZ-eqZ8" target="_blank">is now live</a>. Head to <a href="https://forums.obsidian.net/topic/96258-update-45-sailing-the-deadfire-archipelago/">the forums</a> to join in on the conversation.</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Coming to Consoles This Holiday Season!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">February 7, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	In the wake of the <a href="http://eternity.obsidian.net/news/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-news-coverage-wrap-up">news coverage</a> yesterday, we are very <a href="http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2018/02/06/pillars-of-eternity-ii-deadfire-coming-to-consoles.aspx" target="_blank">excited to announce</a> that through our publishing partner, Versus Evil, Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire will be coming to the Switch, PS4, and Xbox One this holiday season!</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Update 44 is Now Live!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">February 2, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	The <a href="https://forums.obsidian.net/topic/95892-update-44-making-pillars-ii-gorgeous/">latest Backer Update</a> for Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire is now live. Find out <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iFpzTTlTsV0" target="_blank">what went into</a> making Pillars II gorgeous.</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Coming April 3rd! Pre-orders available now!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">January 25, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	We are excited to announce that Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire will be launching on April, 3rd! You can pre-order the game now from <a href="https://eternity.obsidian.net/buy">Obsidian.net</a>, <a href="https://www.gog.com/game/pillars_of_eternity_ii_deadfire">GOG.com</a>, and <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/560130/Pillars_of_Eternity_II_Deadfire/">Steam</a>.</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Obsidian and Versus Evil Partnering With THQ Nordic For Physical Distribution of Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">January 23, 2018</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	Today THQ Nordic and Versus Evil <a href="https://thqnordic.com/article/thq-nordic-and-versus-evil-sign-exclusive-distribution-deal-obsidian-entertainments-pillars" target="_blank">announced their partnership</a> for the physical distribution of Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire to retailers!</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" alt="Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire" src="/images/stories/deadfire-64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire Update 43 Is Live!</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">December 22, 2017</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	As the holidays approach, it&#39;s time to take stock, look back, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36oY8b3lkt0" target="_blank">and be amazed</a> at the awesome year we&#39;ve had making Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire and sharing with you all in <a href="https://forums.obsidian.net/topic/95285-update-43-the-year-in-review">Update 43</a>.</p></div>
			</li>
					<li class="news-row">
				<div class="news-field-icon">
										<img width="64" height="64" title="Obsidian" alt="Obsidian" src="/images/stories/obsidian_64x64.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="news-field-title">PCGamesN Interviews Leonard Boyarsky On His Career In Games</div>
				<div class="news-field-date">December 15, 2017</div>
				<div class="news-field-body"><p>
	The folks over at PCGamesN recently got a chance to sit down with Leonard Boyarsky and <a href="https://www.pcgamesn.com/leonard-boyarsky-new-obsidian-game-vampire-making-of-diablo-3-story" target="_blank">got to know</a> about his incredible career in video games!</p></div>
			</li>
				</ul>
